Binary Sentiment Classification of News (Good vs. Bad)
Objective:
Build a machine learning model that classifies news headlines or short texts as Good (positive impact) or Bad (negative impact).


use pre-built news datasets  AG News Corpus and label a subset manually.
Download the dataset
Manually relabel a subset (or use keywords) to map news to "Good" or "Bad"

 Logistic Regression (Scikit-learn)
- TF-IDF Vectorization
- Confusion Matrix & Evaluation Metrics
- (Optional: VADER for weak supervision)
- Python, Pandas, Matplotlib
